<subSubSection pageId="74" pageNumber="75" type="ecology">
<paragraph pageId="74" pageNumber="75">Ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="74" pageNumber="75">The species is found in disturbed areas between 0-2,200 m elevation in its native range, but around cities and cultivated fields from sea level to 700 m in North America.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
